title: SC EP:811 The Thermal Camera Incident
itunes:title: SC EP:811 The Thermal Camera Incident
description: Tonight I will be speaking to Greg and Charles. The guys were hiking in the Daniel Boone National Forest at night when they had an encounter with a creature. The men were able to see the creature through Greg's thermal camera. The night did not end there.
